---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BrandBranchesGrid from '../../components/BrandBranchesGrid.astro';
import { MAIN_PHONE, MAIN_PHONE_TEL } from '../../data/branches';

const title = "Jenn-Air Range Hood Repair | Southern California | Downdraft + Obsidian";
const description = "Jenn-Air range hood repair across Southern California — JXD downdraft pioneer + JXW wall + Rise/Obsidian/Noir design lines. Whirlpool Corp since 2004. $89 diagnostic. (424) 325-0520.";
const canonical = "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/jennair-range-hood-repair/";

const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Who owns Jenn-Air today?",
    a: "<b>Jenn-Air is a Whirlpool Corporation brand</b> (Benton Harbor MI) since Whirlpool acquired Maytag in 2006 — Jenn-Air came into the Whirlpool portfolio as part of the Maytag Corporation acquisition (Jenn-Air had been a Maytag brand since 1982). Before that, Jenn-Air was founded 1961 in Indianapolis by Louis J. Jenn, most famous for inventing the <b>residential downdraft ventilation</b> system in 1965 — the first practical downdraft for a home range, which remains Jenn-Air's signature engineering contribution to the category. Today Jenn-Air sits at the premium + design-forward tier of Whirlpool Corp's residential portfolio, pitched as the Whirlpool-family luxury alternative to Sub-Zero Group (Wolf) + BSH (Thermador) + Middleby (Viking)."
  },
  {
    q: "What makes Jenn-Air downdraft distinct from other brands?",
    a: "Jenn-Air pioneered the residential downdraft in 1965 and remains the category's most-associated brand — when buyers think \"downdraft ventilation,\" they think Jenn-Air. <b>JXD downdraft series</b> (30-inch electric + gas variants) raises on a motor-lift mechanism from behind the cooktop when cooking, then retracts when finished. Same concept Jenn-Air has been iterating for 60 years, now with quieter blower motors + smarter controls. Competing downdrafts (Wolf Pro Island downdraft, Broan TBPN, Best by Broan, Bosch, Zephyr Presrv) all reference the Jenn-Air category — though each brand has its own engineering variation. For service, the Jenn-Air downdraft is the install type our LA techs have the deepest specialty knowledge on."
  },
  {
    q: "Jenn-Air downdraft motor-lift mechanism stuck — diagnostic?",
    a: "Most common Jenn-Air downdraft fault. The motor-lift raises the vent from behind the cooktop + retracts back down. Failure modes: (1) lift motor gearbox wear at 10-12 year mark; lift motor swap $420–$620; (2) lift-mechanism mechanical obstruction — kitchen debris (food, utensils) falling into the retraction slot; obstruction clear $140–$220; (3) lift sensor / limit switch fault; sensor swap $220–$340; (4) control-board lift-circuit capacitor; board swap $480–$680; (5) blower motor (separate from lift motor — runs when downdraft is up) $380–$540. Our techs carry Jenn-Air downdraft-specific lift mechanism parts. Whirlpool Corp Benton Harbor parts chain supports 2-4 day LA lead on common service items."
  },
  {
    q: "Obsidian + Rise + Noir — what are these Jenn-Air design lines?",
    a: "Jenn-Air relaunched its design-forward positioning in 2018 with three style collections: <b>Rise</b> (modern transitional — stainless with black trim), <b>Noir</b> (all-black matte), <b>Obsidian</b> (all-black with graphite tones). These are style lineups spanning Jenn-Air's full residential kitchen appliance portfolio including range hoods. Our range-hood service scope covers all three collections at the hood + downdraft level — the design differences are cosmetic (finish + trim + knobs) while the underlying ventilation + motor + controls engineering is shared. When ordering parts we verify the collection variant to match hardware + trim; core mechanical parts cross-fit across all three."
  },
  {
    q: "Jenn-Air vs Wolf vs Viking vs Thermador luxury pro-hoods?",
    a: "Four luxury pro-hood positioning options. <b>Jenn-Air (this page)</b> — Whirlpool Corp premium tier; downdraft specialty; Rise/Noir/Obsidian design lineup; JXW wall series + JXD downdraft. <b>Wolf</b> — Sub-Zero Group Madison WI; Sub-Zero/Wolf/Cove coordinated suite integration; see <a href='/brands/wolf-range-hood-repair/'>Wolf range hood</a>. <b>Viking</b> — Middleby Greenwood MS; VWH wall + color program; see <a href='/brands/viking-range-hood-repair/'>Viking range hood</a>. <b>Thermador</b> — BSH Irvine CA parts warehouse proximity; Masterpiece + Pro Grand lineup; see <a href='/brands/thermador-range-hood-repair/'>Thermador range hood</a>. LA choice drivers: Jenn-Air for downdraft specialty or Whirlpool-family coordination; the others for specific matched-suite context."
  },
  {
    q: "Jenn-Air Wi-Fi connectivity — JennAir Connect app issue or hood?",
    a: "Newer Jenn-Air hoods (2019+) integrate with <b>JennAir Connect</b> (app-brand Wi-Fi ecosystem that also covers KitchenAid Connect + Whirlpool Connect on the Whirlpool Corp side). Connectivity fault triage: (1) restart home router + modem — resolves most \"app can't find hood\" issues without appliance service; (2) re-pair hood to JennAir Connect via the app — pull power to hood 60 seconds + re-pair; (3) verify router is on 2.4 GHz band (Jenn-Air hood Wi-Fi radio is 2.4 GHz only — dual-band routers can push traffic to 5 GHz which the module can't receive); (4) firmware update via app if available. If all four steps fail + disconnection persists, the hood's Wi-Fi module may have failed; replacement $220–$340 installed. Most connectivity calls resolve at steps 1-3."
  },
  {
    q: "Residential Jenn-Air vs commercial exhaust?",
    a: "Jenn-Air makes <b>residential</b> range hoods — this page's scope (JXW wall 30-48 inch + JXD downdraft + Rise/Noir/Obsidian design variants). For commercial restaurant / foodservice kitchen exhaust (Captive-Aire / Halton / Greenheck / Gaylord at 2000+ CFM with grease-duct + makeup air integration), see <a href='/commercial/exhaust-hood-repair/'>commercial exhaust hood repair</a>. Different scope, different parts chain."
  },
  {
    q: "What does Jenn-Air range hood repair cost in LA?",
    a: "Residential diagnostic $89 waived with repair. Typical Jenn-Air bands: JXD downdraft lift motor $420–$620 (signature service item); JXD blower motor $380–$540; lift sensor / limit switch $220–$340; JXW wall variable-speed motor $320–$480; control-board $380–$620; Wi-Fi module (JennAir Connect models) $220–$340; grease-filter latch $120–$200; LED light assembly $220–$340; Rise/Noir/Obsidian trim replacement $180–$320 (cosmetic service); baffle-filter replacement $40–$100 per filter. Jenn-Air hood service runs mid-luxury pricing — above Broan/Whirlpool Corp mass-market, slightly below Wolf/Viking/Thermador luxury top tier. Whirlpool Corp Benton Harbor parts support 2-4 day LA lead on common items."
  }
];

const schemaJsons = [
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "LocalBusiness", "@id": canonical + "#business",
    "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair — Jenn-Air Range Hood Service",
    "image": "https://samedayappliance.repair/images/same-day-appliance-repair.png",
    "url": canonical, "telephone": MAIN_PHONE_TEL, "priceRange": "$$"
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "Service", "serviceType": "Jenn-Air Range Hood Repair",
    "provider": { "@id": canonical + "#business" },
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ],
    "description": "Jenn-Air range hood repair across LA — JXD downdraft pioneer, JXW wall 30-48 inch, Rise/Noir/Obsidian design collections, JennAir Connect Wi-Fi integration. Whirlpool Corporation brand (via 2006 Maytag acquisition); downdraft category founder 1965. $89 residential diagnostic waived with repair.",
    "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "priceSpecification": { "@type": "PriceSpecification", "price": "89.00", "priceCurrency": "USD", "description": "Residential diagnostic fee, waived with repair" } }
  },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({ "@type": "Question", "name": f.q, "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": f.a } })) },
  { "@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Brands", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Jenn-Air", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/jennair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 4, "name": "Jenn-Air Range Hood Repair", "item": canonical }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Fragment slot="head-scripts">{schemaJsons.map((schema) => (<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />))}</Fragment>
  <div class="call-banner"><div class="wrap"><span>Jenn-Air range hood service? Same-day across LA:</span><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a></div></div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Jenn-Air › Range Hood Repair</div>
    <h1>Jenn-Air Range Hood Repair</h1>
    <p class="lede">Jenn-Air is a <b>Whirlpool Corporation</b> brand (Benton Harbor MI) since the 2006 Maytag acquisition — Jenn-Air itself founded 1961 Indianapolis by Louis J. Jenn, who <b>invented the residential downdraft in 1965</b>. The JXD downdraft remains Jenn-Air's signature category product; JXW wall 30-48 inch covers conventional hood lineup; 2018 Rise / Noir / Obsidian design collections span finish + trim variants across the portfolio. 2019+ hoods integrate JennAir Connect Wi-Fi. Our LA range-hood techs carry Jenn-Air downdraft-specific lift mechanism parts + JXW service components; Whirlpool Corp Benton Harbor parts chain supports 2-4 day LA lead. Same-day dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta"><a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a><a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a></div>
