      <li><b>Downdraft inventor 1965</b> — Louis J. Jenn; category signature product</li>
      <li><b>Whirlpool Corp since 2006</b> — via Maytag acquisition; premium-tier brand</li>
      <li><b>Rise / Noir / Obsidian design lineup</b> — 2018+ style collections</li>
      <li><b>$89 residential diagnostic</b> — waived when you authorize the repair</li>
    </ul>
  </div></section>

  <BrandBranchesGrid />

  <section class="trust-bar"><div class="wrap"><span>CSLB #1138898 · Insured</span><span>Same-day in 5 SoCal counties</span><span>Residential diagnostic $89 · waived with repair</span></div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Jenn-Air range hood failures our techs see most often in LA</h2>
