    <div class="fail-block"><h3>JXD blower motor (separate from lift)</h3><p>Blower swap $380–$540.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>Lift sensor / limit switch</h3><p>Downdraft position sensing. $220–$340.</p></div>
    <div class="fail-block"><h3>JXW wall variable-speed motor</h3><p>Wall-series capacitor failure 10-15 year. Motor $320–$480.</p></div>
