  <section class="section"><div class="wrap">
    <h2>Jenn-Air range hood product lines we service</h2>
    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card"><h3>JXD downdraft 30"</h3><p>Downdraft pioneer lineup. Electric + gas variants. Motor-lift mechanism signature.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>JXW wall 30-48 inch</h3><p>Conventional wall-mount hood. Premium residential tier.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Rise collection</h3><p>Stainless + black trim modern transitional. 2018 design-forward relaunch.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Noir collection</h3><p>All-black matte finish. Tool-integrated trim lineup.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>Obsidian collection</h3><p>All-black with graphite tones. Premium upgrade tier.</p></div>
      <div class="model-card"><h3>JennAir Connect (2019+)</h3><p>Wi-Fi integration with Whirlpool Corp ecosystem. Shared app with KitchenAid Connect + Whirlpool Connect.</p></div>
