  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>JXD downdraft — the Jenn-Air specialty</h2>
    <p>Jenn-Air invented the residential downdraft in 1965 and remains the most-associated brand with the category. The JXD downdraft lifts from behind the cooktop via motor-lift mechanism when cooking starts, then retracts when finished. 60 years of iteration has improved motor quieting + control intelligence but the core mechanism concept is unchanged. Our LA downdraft service experience concentrates on JXD units — they're the most common downdraft install across LA. Competing downdrafts (Wolf Pro Island, Broan TBPN, Best by Broan, Zephyr Presrv) all reference the Jenn-Air category but each brand has engineering variation; the diagnostic approach varies by brand.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Jenn-Air vs luxury pro-hood alternatives (Wolf / Viking / Thermador)</h2>
    <p>Four luxury pro-hood brands in LA. Jenn-Air sits at the Whirlpool Corp premium tier with downdraft specialty signature + Rise/Noir/Obsidian design lineup. <a href="/brands/wolf-range-hood-repair/">Wolf</a> (Sub-Zero Group Madison WI coordinated-suite), <a href="/brands/viking-range-hood-repair/">Viking</a> (Middleby Greenwood MS heritage + color program), <a href="/brands/thermador-range-hood-repair/">Thermador</a> (BSH Irvine CA proximity). LA choice drivers: Jenn-Air for downdraft or Whirlpool-family (Whirlpool + KitchenAid + Maytag + Amana + Jenn-Air single-call), the others for their respective matched-suite positioning.</p>
  </div></section>

  <section class="section alt"><div class="wrap narrow">
    <h2>Residential Jenn-Air vs commercial exhaust</h2>
